OL,6,GOn Saturday morning, Studio B in
OL,7,GBelfast was the base for the BBC's TV
OL,8,Gcoverage of the local elections in
OL,9,GNorthern Ireland, with Mark
OL,10,GCarruthers anchoring.
OL,12,FThere were live link-ups with
OL,13,Freporters and politicians at the
OL,14,Fvarious count centres across Northern
OL,15,FIreland.  Studio presentation
OL,16,Fincluded the use of a green-screen
OL,17,Farea for results graphics.
OL,3,CBBC/UTV local election 2023
