OL,6,FThe large video wall in Studio B
OL,7,Fdisplayed imagery of the multi-
OL,8,Fcoloured hexagon device, also used by
OL,9,Fthe BBC for national elections and
OL,10,Fcoverage of local elections in other
OL,11,Fparts of the UK.
OL,13,FLower-thirds were a simpler strain of
OL,14,Fthose used for the recent coverage of
OL,15,Flocal elections in England.
OL,17,FBBC Northern Ireland's TV coverage
OL,18,Fwas reduced to a three-hour slot on
OL,19,FSaturday morning, due to industrial
OL,20,Faction by members of the National
OL,21,FUnion of Journalists.
