OL,6,FPlanned coverage on TV and radio on
OL,7,FFriday was blacked out by the strike
OL,8,Faction.
OL,10,FIn UTV land, a more basic graphical/
OL,11,Fpresentation offering by comparison.
OL,12,F The local station utilised the UTV
OL,13,FLive set, with the addition of Vote
OL,14,F23 imagery on the screens at the back
OL,15,Fof the set.
OL,17,FOn the graphics front, we had a
OL,18,Fsimple lower-third scorecard and a
OL,19,Ffull-screen State of the Parties
OL,20,Fgraphic. We didn't spot any council-
OL,21,Fspecific graphics.
