OL,6,FOutside of UTV Live programmes,
OL,7,Felection coverage was confined to a
OL,8,Ftwo-hour slot ` 4pm ` 6pm ` on Friday.
OL,10,FThe coverage included live reporting
OL,11,Fby UTV reporters at the local count
OL,12,Fcentres and interviews with
OL,13,Fpoliticians. And there was in-studio
OL,14,Fanalysis from various political
OL,15,Fcommentators.
